# X/Twitter API Credentials Configuration
# =======================================
#
# Required for search/read endpoints:
CONSUMER_KEY=your_api_key_here
SECRET_KEY=your_api_secret_here
BEARER_TOKEN=your_bearer_token_here

#
#(needed for user-context actions like posting/liking):
X_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_access_token_here
X_ACCESS_SECRET=your_access_token_here

